lines.text: This movie would not be happening without ME!
You fire all the white trash off this movie or I'm walking!
Get off that stage, you stupid bimbo, lemme show you how it's done!
They should teach these people to walk in English.
To put it in layman's terms, take a hike, princess!
If you keep feeding me like this, I'll no longer be a body double but a *double body*!
Sorry, Mister Mogul, my script and my body are not for sale!
